Changes to [SQL] Module
+ Expose transaction management into the hand of programmer via [BeginTransaction],[Commit] and [Rollback], which is more convenient when it come to custom implementation or to proxy the connector.
- Due to transaction now being managed by programmer, the second overload (string connectionString,bool UseTransaction) has been removed from DataConnector
+ ExpressionTranslator now support string.IsNullOrEmpty/Whitespace translation.

Add new module [DesignPattern]
+ This module aimed to utilize functionality inside this library by provide generator to generate code boilerplate for design pattern
+ This build is coming with UnitOfWork generator (and more later)


